nodes.text: A planet was a rocky and mountainous place. During the Imperial Era; Sabine Wren, Hera Syndulla and Chopper came here to steal a medical kit from a Lambda class shuttle. Stormtroopers steal the shuttle while chasing them. However, Sabine and Hera stole the wrong shuttle. Chopper then took the right shuttle and took Sabine and Hera to his own shuttle, that is, the right shuttle, and they go away.
